<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>SME Assist AI | AI Customer Support for Small Businesses</title>
  <meta name="description" content="SME Assist AI helps small businesses reply to customer enquiries faster with an affordable AI chatbot solution." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <p class="eyebrow"><i class="fa-solid fa-robot"></i> AI customer support for SMEs</p>
          <h1>AI Customer Support for Small Businesses</h1>
          <p class="hero-text">Help your business reply to customer enquiries instantly, 24/7, without needing extra manpower.</p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/demo">Try Demo</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#features">View Features</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-badges">
            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Instant replies</span>
            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Easy to launch</span>
            <span><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Budget-friendly</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card">
          <div class="chat-preview">
            <div class="chat-header">
              <h3>Live Preview</h3>
              <span class="status-dot"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="preview-messages">
              <div class="message customer">
                <span>Customer:</span>
                <p>What time do you close today?</p>
              </div>
              <div class="message bot">
                <span>Bot:</span>
                <p>We close at 9 PM today. Would you like to make a booking?</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="stats-section">
      <div class="container stats-grid">
        <article class="stat-card">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i>
          <h3>24/7 instant replies</h3>
          <p>Customers get answers even outside business hours.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="stat-card">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-people-group"></i>
          <h3>Less manual workload</h3>
          <p>Your team spends less time answering the same questions.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="stat-card">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-smile"></i>
          <h3>Better customer experience</h3>
          <p>Faster replies help build trust and keep customers engaged.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="problem" class="section">
      <div class="container section-grid">
        <div>
          <p class="section-label">The problem</p>
          <h2>Many small businesses lose opportunities when replies are slow</h2>
          <p>SMEs receive many repeated questions every day. Owners and staff are often busy serving customers, so enquiries can be missed or answered late. When that happens, potential sales and customer trust can be lost.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-card">
          <ul>
            <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Repeated questions take time to answer</li>
            <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Busy staff may miss customer enquiries</li>
            <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Slow replies can lead to lost revenue</li>
            <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i> Manual responses create extra effort</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="how-it-works" class="section alt-bg">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="section-label">How it works</p>
          <h2>Simple steps, clear value</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="card-grid three-up">
          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-comment-dots"></i></div>
            <h3>Step 1: Customer asks a question</h3>
            <p>A customer sends a common enquiry such as opening hours or pricing.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-brain"></i></div>
            <h3>Step 2: AI chatbot understands the enquiry</h3>
            <p>The chatbot quickly identifies the request and prepares a helpful response.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-paper-plane"></i></div>
            <h3>Step 3: Customer receives an instant reply</h3>
            <p>Customers get fast support while your team stays focused on higher-value tasks.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features" class="section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="section-label">Features</p>
          <h2>Support more customers with less effort</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="card-grid four-up">
          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i></div>
            <h3>FAQ automation</h3>
            <p>Answer common questions instantly without repeating yourself.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i></div>
            <h3>Opening hours replies</h3>
            <p>Help customers know when you are available at any time of day.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-tag"></i></div>
            <h3>Product and pricing information</h3>
            <p>Share key details quickly so customers can decide faster.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check"></i></div>
            <h3>Booking enquiry support</h3>
            <p>Guide customers through appointment or booking requests.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-box"></i></div>
            <h3>Order status support</h3>
            <p>Provide simple updates for customers waiting on deliveries.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-tie"></i></div>
            <h3>Human staff escalation</h3>
            <p>When needed, the chatbot can connect customers to a real person.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="icon-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen-button"></i></div>
            <h3>Multi-channel support placeholder</h3>
            <p>A flexible area ready for future website, WhatsApp, or social media integration.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="benefits" class="section alt-bg">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-heading">
          <p class="section-label">Benefits</p>
          <h2>Practical value for growing businesses</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="card-grid two-up">
          <article class="benefit-card">
            <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i> Saves time</h3>
            <p>Automate common enquiries so your team can focus on important work.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="benefit-card">
            <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-repeat"></i> Reduces repeated replies</h3>
            <p>One chatbot can answer the same questions again and again.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="benefit-card">
            <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-gauge-high"></i> Improves response speed</h3>
            <p>Customers receive answers promptly, even when your team is busy.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="benefit-card">
            <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i> Prevents missed enquiries</h3>
            <p>Customers are less likely to be ignored when support is always available.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="benefit-card">
            <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i> Provides consistent answers</h3>
            <p>Customers receive clear and reliable information every time.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="benefit-card">
            <h3><i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-trend-up"></i> Supports business growth</h3>
            <p>Better support helps you serve more customers without increasing costs drastically.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container cta-card">
        <h2>Ready to automate your customer support?</h2>
        <p>See how a simple chatbot can help your business respond faster and serve customers better.</p>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/demo">Try Demo</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
